Pakistan May Increase Natural Gas Tariff Today, Spokesman Says

-- B y   K h u r r u m   A n i s
-- 
2011-06-30T07:39:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-30/pakistan-may-increase-natural-gas-tariff-today-spokesman-says.html
Pakistan  may increase the tariff for
natural gas by 15 percent for domestic consumers, said Irfan
Qazi, public relations officer to the minister for Petroleum and
Natural Resources.  “The summary for the increase will be sent to the
country’s finance committee for approval today,” Qazi said in a
phone interview. “It should be implemented from July 1.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Khurrum Anis in Karachi at 
 kkhan14@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
David Merritt in Mumbai at 
 dmerritt1@bloomberg.net  